       Bloody Streets is a 2D top-down brutal and challenging shooter game     
       with lots of blood. The game has been developed by our indie game       
       development team, Headless Wizard.                                      
       It is a modern remake of classic top down shooter formulas and our      
       goal was to reinvent the feel of the old arcade games with the          
       desired quality by the players today.                                   
                                                                               
       Game main features are:                                                 
       - Fast paced arcade style action                                        
       - Use of the environment as weapons in combat                           
       - Unique art style                                                      
       - Traditional frame by frame animations                                 
       - Music dynamic rhythm system                                           
                                                                               
       The game made using our game engine based on XNA API and we did a lot   
       of optimization to reach high fame rate.Focusing on a PC game led us    
       to handle lots of enemies, destructions, physical simulations to make   
       this game exciting. Bloody Streets has high level of detail in          
       gameplay, visual and player experience.                                 
                                                                               
                                                                               
